Honey Trehan was born on October 4, 1978 in Sagar, Madhya Pradesh, India. He is a casting director and assistant director, known for Raat Akeli Hai (2020)
Honey Trehan is a Bollywood casting director, producer, and assistant director, who is associated with the industry for more than two decades.
